 March Monday 12 1917 . Rain last night . Reg turn up meet me . He is onli about a mile down the road . Took me along to see Ern . Murray who is stay a few day at a collect post preparatori to go to Amien about his eye . ' Twas great to meet them . Had not long for a yarn , but Reg invit us down to tea Wed . even . Also met Nether Bill Johnston . Receiv big mail 18 letter . Baghdad fallen .
